title: Dakine Campus 33L Street Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Campus 33L Street Pack in Gradient.
Campus 33L Street Pack Features:
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 15" laptops
- Insulated cooler pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Mesh side pockets
- Adjustable sternum strap
